restrict_one.description: Only one accordion item is open at once.

require_role.description: Comma separated list of user role which is required.

hide_on_role.description: Comma separated user roles hides content if exists.

alternative_image.description: Choose different image if content is portrait ratio.

priority.description: When true, the image will be considered high priority and preload. Should only be used when the image is visible above the fold.

disable_lazy_loading.description: Note: if priority is enabled lazy loading will always be disabled.

image_focal_point.description: Focal point in X,Y coordinates in % of the original image. Example center top: "50x0",  center bottom: "50x100", top left: "0x0", right middle: "100x50"

disable_smart_crop.description: By default smart crop and face recognition is enabled. On demand you can disable the functionality.

background_elements.description: Background color must be last in list! Don't mix too many elements into each other it won't have the right effect.

border_radius.description: Set border for all corners - "4px"  or any other style. Order is: top-left,top-right,bottom-right,bottom-left. Full example: "24px 0 24px 0"

value.description: Paste any ready to use gradient background property into the value field.

size.description: Will be overwritten if "Size Fixed" is in use.

size_fixed.description: Overwrites "Size" cover/contain to a fixed size. Example: "100px 50px"

open_external.description: Opens external links in new tab. Only works for external not internal links.

body.description: Leave empty if used as options of "List Widget" element.

action_width.description: Width as CSS statement: 400px or 30% or 30vw

tag_reference.description: Don't use this any more! Use instead CONFIG => Tag

dateStyle.description: If any date time style is used, all other properties will be ignored - they can not be mixed.

width.description: Width in % of the current available space. Default is 100%

path.description:
The price of the path is available for button labels or headline text of the trigger element:
{price} {discount} {total}

sdk_client_id.description: Defaults to the paypal sandbox app

product_title.description: Change the design of the product title

cart_footer_additional.description: Additional information between footer headline and checkout button

end.description: End date can be empty in case of full day events.

multiple_event_dates.description: If an event has mutliple dates, the start and end should select the first and last possible event date.

scroll_to_time.description: Scroll to a time in case you enable week or day view.

api.description: Go to the google form and copy iframe src url

success_body.description: This will be shown after the form was submitted successfully, replacing the form elements.

error_msg_required.description: Text to be displayed if a required field is empty. Default is: 'This field is required'

fields_min_width.description: Min width in pixel for the Field Elements

form_inline.description: Show all form fields in one row.

promotion.description: Top page content visible on every page. You can disable the content on page level.

setup_language.description: Set language for the project. Sets <html lang="[language]">

setup_supported_languages.description: Comma separated list of all supported languages. Sets header response "Content-Language".

setup_facebook_pixel.description: Pixel, can be multiple IDs comma separated.

toolbar_background.description: Enable CSS background property for using gradients or any other background setting.

seo_website_url.description: Full website URL without leading slash: https://google.com

seo_robots.description: Set robots 'index,follow'. Important if site goes public

toolbar_elevation.description: A value between 0-24. Defaults to "4". Disable elevation with "0".

max_lines.description: The max number of lines use "line-clamp" property and truncates text at a specific number of lines.

newsletter_subscription.description: Add newsletter ID only if no checkbox to consent is used (legitimate process)

consent_communication.description: Creates checkbox for:  "consent to communicate" (agrees to receive newsletter)

consent_process.description: If form requires a checkbox to proceed: "consent to process"

legitimate_interest.description: Contact is legitimate request. Does not render any checkbox and legitimates newsletter directly. Overwrites consent checkboxes if selected. Only renders if "consent process" and "consent communication" is empty.

icon_url.description: Icon Url to a public SVG file

color.description: If SVG image is used sets the fill color. If PNG is used it sets background color for fit-in image crop. Hex or "transparent"

mobile_breakpoint.description: Only use this option inside of header toolbars

layout.description: Modify look and feel of the list. Switches between "news", "lists", "card" and "links"

enable_min_height.description: Useful to set this option if the list is part of a search with an enabled right navigation drawer.

tags.description: Use "Category" instead in order to make sure that renaming of tags works. Otherwise check list widgets after rename.

match_all_tags.description: If multiple tags are selected, all tags must match the criteria.

threshold.description: Percentage of the target's visibility the observer's callback should be executed. Value between 0 - 100

slide_direction.description: Direction for "slide" animation. "up" better only if its last element of a section. "down" if its the first element of a section.

enable_overflow.description: Enable slide overflow from website body and not content section

meta_robots.description: Disable page index (overwrite the website setting)

url.description: Any Youtube, Vimeo or other URL

reverse_on_mobile.description: This option use column reverse for mobile view.

reverse_on_tablet.description: This option use column reverse for tablet view.

section_identifier.description: Sets the ID for the content section. you can use #ID-NAME in the URL to start at that scroll position

background_style.description: Fixed background is "parallax" effect that the image does not scroll. Use "Fixed image" if its first element or "Fixed cover" on any other section. Disabled on all mobile/tablet devices.

video_ratio.description: Set the video ratio of the element. Defaults to 16/9

area_served.description: Comma separated list of served areas: US, DE, CA

available_language.description: Comma separated list of languages: English, French, German

price_currency.description: 3 letter ISO standard: EUR, USD, CAD ...

same_as.description: Comma separated list of urls to the social profile: 'http://www.facebook.com/your-profile', 'http://instagram.com/yourProfile'

section_variant.description: Preset of the section value. Only works if the child of the slide element is a section.

button_top_align.description: On larger snackbars it might be better to show the close action buttons to the top

auto_show.description: Show the snackbar in x ms. Default to false

auto_close.description: Hide in x ms. 5000 is 5 sec. Default: none

box_shadow.description: Only applies if elevation is empty.

z_index.description: Use the property z-index if you want to overlay an element with negative margin and it is not visible.

align.description: Don't use "Full Height" property in order to make this option taking effect.
